      <abstract>
        <p>TEI XML compliant "Comprehensive Coptic Lexicon" including both original Egyptian-Coptic
          lemmata and loanwords from ancient Greek. Joint release of the BBAW Academy research
          project "Strukturen und Transformationen des Wortschatzes der ägyptischen Sprache",
          Berlin-Brandenburgische Akademie der Wissenschaften, Berlin and the "Database and
          Dictionary of Greek Loanwords in Coptic (DDGLC)" project, Freie Universität Berlin. </p>
      </abstract>
